@node "History" "History"

            @{b}Release History@{ub}

1.12 (5.1.97)
    Added support for the Forward events type of Thor 2.4

1.11 (15.09.96)
    Changed Bcc: header to bcc: to avoid a bug in Thor 2.3/2.31

1.10 (14.08.96)
    Fixed a small bug that caused a bogus header to be created if you
    selected Add New Header and then Cancel

1.0  (05.08.96)
    First release version
